\c 1
\s Vanhu vanorairwa kuvaka tembere
\p
\v 1 Mugore ramambo Dhariyasi mambo, mumwedzi wechitanhatu, muzuva rekutanga remwedzi, rakasvika shoko raJehovha nemuporofita Hagai kuna Zerubhabheri mwanakomana waShearitieri, mubati waJudha, nekuna Joshua mwanakomana waJehozadhaki, mupristi mukuru, richiti:
\v 2 Anotaura seizvi Jehovha wehondo: Vanhu ava vanoti: Nguva haina kusvika, nguva imba yaJehovha yaichavakwa.
\v 3 Ipapo shoko raJehovha rakasvika neruoko rwaHagai muporofita, richiti:
\v 4 Haisi nguva yenyu here, imwi pachenyu, kuti mugare mudzimba dzenyu dzakafukidzwa mukati nemapuranga, asi imba ino idongo?
\v 5 Naizvozvo ikozvino, znoreva seizvi Jehovha wehondo: Isai moyo wenyu panzira dzenyu.
\v 6 Makadzvara zvakawanda, ai makapinza zvishoma, munodya, asi hamuguti, munonwa, asi hamugungwi, munozvipfekedza, asi hakuna anodziirwa, neanotambira muhoro anotambirira muhoro muchikwama chakabooka.
\p
\v 7 Anoreva seizvi Jehovha wehondo: Isai moyo wenyu panzira dzenyu.
\v 8 Kwirai kuugomo, mugouya nematanda, mugovaka imba, zvino ndichaifarira, uye ndichakudzwa, anoreva Jehovha.
\v 9 Manga makatarisira zvizhinji, asi tarirai, zvishoma, uye pamakaunza kumba, neni ndakafuridza. Nemhaka yei?, anoreva Jehovha wehondo. Nemhaka yeimba yangu yava dongo, zvakadaro imwi munomhanyira umwe neumwe kuimba yake.
\v 10 Naizvozvo matenga pamusoro penyu anonyima kuti kusava nedova, nevhu rinonyima zvibereko zvaro.
\v 11 Zvino ndakadana kuoma pamusoro penyika, nepamusoro pemakomo, nepamusoro pezviyo, nepamusoro pewaini itsva, nepamusoro pemafuta, nepamusoro pechinobudiswa nevhu, nepamusoro pevanhu, nepamusoro pemombe, nepamusoro pebasa rese remaoko.
\p
\v 12 Ipapo Zerubhabheri mwanakomana waShearitieri, naJoshua mwanakomana waJehozadhaki mupristi mukuru, nevakasara vese vevanhu, vakateerera inzwi raJehovha Mwari wavo, nemashoko aHagai muporofita, Jehovha Mwari wavo sezvaiva amutuma, vanhu ndokutya pamberi paJehovha.
\v 13 Zvino wakataura Hagai mutumwa waJehovha neshoko raJehovha kuvanhu achiti: Ndinemwi, anoreva Jehovha.
\v 14 Jehovha ndokumutsa mweya waZerubhabheri mwanakomana waShearitieri, mubati waJudha, nemweya waJoshua mwanakomana waJehozadhaki, mupristi mukuru, nemweya wevakasara vese vevanhu, zvino vakauya ndokushanda muimba yaJehovha wehondo, Mwari wavo,
\v 15 pazuva remakumi maviri nemana remwedzi wechitanhatu, pagore raDhariyasi mambo.
